  dialogueLines:
  - <speed=10><emotion=dismiss>You're <size=80%>late</size>, <color=#FFD700>my friend</color>.
  - <emotion=angry><speed=30><b>Three days</b> past due. I don't like <color=#FF0000>waiting</color>.
  - <speed=8><pause=0.5><emotion=nervous>My <i>associates</i> are getting <size=120%>impatient</size>.
  - <emotion=happy><speed=25><color=#FFD700>But...</color> I'm a <b>reasonable</b>
    man. <pause=0.3><speed=15>You have <color=#00FF00>48 hours</color>.
